>\n<br />\n和理非都沒用了<br />\n<br />\n唔係分化。。而係事實"},{"pid":"6866141bdd11d145099f53e460d16117a2987cf6","tid":1608293,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:34:51.000Z","msg":"由612開始就冇退路"},{"pid":"ff9a87057574b1be5a515c21174030b86e9b9f5b","tid":1608293,"uid":279994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:37:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直接解散警隊</span></span><br />\n獨立調查委員會冇用啦<br />\n你信仲有白警咩?<br />\n查得幾耐? 三萬個警察逐個問? <br />\n有咩用, 最後拎D出咗名嘅嚟祭旗 最多搭單送幾個大粒出嚟<br />\n有咩用<br />\n直接解散警隊"},{"pid":"245828953aa8351f1c2902505b2597546f6d8b91","tid":1608293,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"回不去，只有向前衝"},{"pid":"771f32c992d8e61c97323021bbe6099c8de1e7bc","tid":1608293,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"245828953aa8351f1c2902505b2597546f6d8b91","tid":1608293,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"回不去，只有向前衝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deccd5dc426e58d6b5da925634c847dacc379c0b","tid":1608293,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"最好攪到香港聽日返唔到工同學<br />\n<br />\n大家攬炒"},{"pid":"bed7d8cab15547ec3841961627c0ad966cf0db65","tid":1608293,"uid":206284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"DLLM 好嬲 好無力 集氣所有手足要無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到呢一步已經要改訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻解散警隊 連同所有高層<br />\n改要求 係要求 唔再係訴求呀<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人 同我記住<br />\n6.9到而加無個黑警負責<br />\n有手足比人虐殺 強姦 <br />\n呢班人渣係唔比FA救人<br />\n到今日已經開咗真槍 有手足中槍<br />\n抱歉呢4個月發生太多事連我自己都記唔住<br />\n但係<br />\n612 615 71 <strong>721</strong> 811 <strong>831</strong> <strong>101</strong>呢啲日子一定要記實<br />\n721 證明班人渣唔係為香港人服務<br />\n831 證明班人渣連人都唔係 係禽獸<br />\n101 港殤日 無國慶 <br />\n回歸中國 對香港人黎講 係最大既痛<br />\n成功之日 香港所有警察必被清算<br />\n白警？咪玩喇 有既一早出咗聲或者遲咗職。<br />\n警隊要團結要紀律？<br />\n咁要清算你地三萬人 一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>BTW 各位和理非<br />\n你地真係覺得成立獨立調查委員會就收貨？<br />\n請你地記得 林鄭月娥唔係你地選 <br />\n佢無必要對香港人負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無真普選 我地都係輸。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n講完<br />\n多謝今日喺海富果班手足<br />\n知有手足走唔甩<br />\n好抱歉我未夠勇<br />\n但幾兇險都好 我都會再出黎<br />\n直至煲底相見果日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de6691d79593642a1c7446ce224b3e8cbe039c9","tid":1608293,"uid":291461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"想革命 想要諗返工 香港人真係.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：聽日返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b127f61bc37696c4e9872ec8e6695292b2966d","tid":1608293,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb9cfcdcb0891d2ab311870532b6fe8c96ad1f33","tid":1608293,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f90b00ba13fa06875017a63ff7736583c4e7e43","tid":1608293,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5818f78313ea28cdd00ca4f38ab3e9df7e76627f","tid":1608293,"uid":268930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcf7e3c66517cb633e11f2f32920282b51fb3c48","tid":1608293,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"唉...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:09:17.000Z","msg":"唔會退<br />\n唔會放棄"},{"pid":"ea4efc7f6ec6a85eebefd3d0e997e29772118c37","tid":1608293,"uid":291461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco